Name: Mechanic Location
maps__Query__c: FROM ServiceResource WHERE Id != '' AND (JobTitle__c = 'Repair Mechanic' OR JobTitle__c = 'Service Mechanic')
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: ServiceResource
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers

Name: S1 Dispatched Service Appointments
maps__Query__c: FROM ServiceAppointment WHERE Id != '' AND (Status = 'Dispatched') AND Priority__c IN ('S1 - Emergency') AND OwnerId IN :TeamRoleIds
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: ServiceAppointment
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers

Name: S2 Dispatched Service Appointments
maps__Query__c: FROM ServiceAppointment WHERE Id != '' AND (Status = 'Dispatched') AND Priority__c IN ('S2 - High') AND OwnerId IN :TeamRoleIds
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: ServiceAppointment
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers

Name: S3 Dispatched Service Appointments
maps__Query__c: FROM ServiceAppointment WHERE Id != '' AND (Status = 'Dispatched') AND Priority__c IN ('S3 - Normal') AND OwnerId IN :TeamRoleIds
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: ServiceAppointment
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers

Name: S4 Dispatched Service Appointments
maps__Query__c: FROM ServiceAppointment WHERE Id != '' AND (Status = 'Dispatched') AND Priority__c IN ('S4 - Low') AND OwnerId IN :TeamRoleIds
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: ServiceAppointment
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers

Name: Buildings with Shutdown Units
maps__Query__c: FROM Location WHERE Id != '' AND Id IN (SELECT LocationId FROM Asset WHERE (OperationalStatus__c = 'Shutdown'))
maps__BaseObject__r.Name: Location
maps__Folder__r.Name: Otis Layers
